On surveillance video, you can see the shooter, who had been parked down the block, drive up to Ricky’s driveway, get out and approach his Ricky who appeared to have spotted the gunman and tried to get away. But Ricky was shot multiple times at close range. He remains in critical condition. Detroit Police released the video in hopes that someone will be able to help them identify the shooter who is described as a black man in his late thirties, standing about 5′ 7″ tall with a thin build. He was wearing a gray hooded jacket and blue jeans.